text: This is a list of monuments in Floriana, Malta, which are listed on the National Inventory of the Cultural Property of the Maltese Islands.National Inventory Register, as well as Grade 1 scheduled properties from the Malta Scheduled Property Register maintained by Malta's Planning Authority.
